<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <GTMHead />
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description}>
    <meta name="keywords" content="The Villages post-construction cleaning, The Villages renovation cleanup, The Villages remodeling cleanup, The Villages active adult construction cleanup Florida">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://palmacleaningco.com/the-villages-post-construction-cleaning">
    
    <!-- Favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles-clean.css?v=3">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "Service",
        "name": "The Villages Post-Construction Cleaning",
        "description": "Professional post-construction cleanup services for The Villages renovation and building projects",
        "provider": {
            "@type": "LocalBusiness",
            "name": "Palma Cleaning",
            "telephone": "(352) 764-4747",
            "url": "https://palmacleaningco.com"
        },
        "areaServed": {
            "@type": "Place",
            "name": "The Villages, Florida"
        },
        "offers": {
            "@type": "Offer",
            "description": "Construction cleanup, renovation cleaning, debris removal, and detailed post-construction sanitization for active adult communities"
        }
    }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <GTMBody />
    <Navigation />

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1 class="hero-title">The Villages Post-Construction Cleaning</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">Professional Cleanup After Villa Improvement Projects</p>
                <p class="hero-description">Specialized post-construction cleaning for The Villages villa renovations, additions, and remodeling projects. Transform your construction site back into the comfortable, guest-ready home you envisioned for your active retirement lifestyle in America's Premier Active Adult Community.</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="/book-now" class="btn btn-primary">Book Now</a>
                    <a href="tel:+13527644747" class="btn btn-secondary">Call (352) 764-4747</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image">
                <div class="hero-placeholder">
                    <i class="fas fa-hard-hat"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">The Villages Post-Construction Cleaning</h2>
            <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 3rem;">
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; text-align: center; line-height: 1.6;">Construction and renovation projects in The Villages require specialized cleanup to restore your villa to its comfortable, guest-ready condition. Our post-construction cleaning service handles everything from debris removal to detailed surface restoration, perfect for active adults ready to enjoy their improved homes and get back to the 3,000+ activities and clubs The Villages offers.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
                <div style="background: #f8fafa; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 15px;">
                    <h3 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><i class="fas fa-hammer" style="color: #ff8057; margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Common Villages Projects</h3>
                    <ul style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8;">
                        <li><strong>Kitchen Updates:</strong> Retirement-friendly renovations</li>
                        <li><strong>Bathroom Renovations:</strong> Accessibility improvements</li>
                        <li><strong>Flooring Installation:</strong> Low-maintenance solutions</li>
                        <li><strong>Lanai Enclosures:</strong> Florida living improvements</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div style="background: #f8fafa; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 15px;">
                    <h3 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><i class="fas fa-tools" style="color: #ff8057; margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Specialty Active Adult Cleanup</h3>
                    <ul style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8;">
                        <li>Dust-free environment restoration</li>
                        <li>Entertainment area preparation</li>
                        <li>Guest space readiness</li>
                        <li>Health-conscious deep sanitization</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about" style="background: #f8fafa;">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Complete Villages Construction Cleanup</h2>
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
                <div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
                    <h4 style="color: #ff8057; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><i class="fas fa-broom" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Debris & Dust Removal</h4>
                    <ul style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">
                        <li>Construction debris complete cleanup</li>
                        <li>Fine dust removal from all surfaces</li>
                        <li>Drywall dust thorough elimination</li>
                        <li>Sawdust and wood particle cleanup</li>
                        <li>Paint drops and splatters</li>
