                        <li>Cabinet and millwork detailing</li>
                        <li>Countertop and surface restoration</li>
                        <li>Appliance cleaning and polishing</li>
                        <li>Baseboard and trim cleaning</li>
                        <li>Switch plate and outlet cleaning</li>
